[{"conversations": [{"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110378_story/VO_CHR_110378_STORY_0006.wav"], "content": "哇啊，這也太大了……！這個房間，我真的可以自己一個人用嗎！？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110378_02.png", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100002_story/VO_CHR_100002_STORY_0011.wav"], "content": "嗯，當然了。在潛入『監獄』之前的這段時間，就好好在這裡養精蓄銳吧。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100002_01.png", "speakerName": "耶魯菲莉絲", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110378_story/VO_CHR_110378_STORY_0045.wav"], "content": "謝謝！……但是，也不能這麼悠哉呢。畢竟有許多事情需要準備。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110378_02.png", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100002_story/VO_CHR_100002_STORY_0014.wav"], "content": "是嗎。那麼，就讓我來幫忙吧。有什麼問題就儘管問我。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100002_01.png", "speakerName": "耶魯菲莉絲", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "看來PANTHER你們的世界和這裡相差非常多，所以應該有不少不懂的事情。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100002_01.png", "speakerName": "耶魯菲莉絲", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110378_story/VO_CHR_110378_STORY_0012.wav"], "content": "就是說啊！其實我真的有點困惑，平常在潛入監獄之前都會買好一些傷藥之類的……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110378_02.png", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "但在這邊就沒辦法靠SOPHIE網購，也沒有藥妝店，所以無法得到藥……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110378_02.png", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100002_story/VO_CHR_100002_STORY_0042.wav"], "content": "網購？藥妝店……？雖然我不是很清楚，總之妳想要傷藥對吧？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100002_01.png", "speakerName": "耶魯菲莉絲", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110378_story/VO_CHR_110378_STORY_0011.wav"], "content": "嗯。只要到了比較大的街區，就會賣了對吧？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110378_02.png", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100002_story/VO_CHR_100002_STORY_0030.wav"], "content": "是沒錯……雖然不是說買不到，但藥草的話搞不好還是直接去摘比較快。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100002_01.png", "speakerName": "耶魯菲莉絲", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110378_story/VO_CHR_110378_STORY_0042.wav"], "content": "藥草！？真的有那種東西嗎！？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110378_02.png", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "……PANTHER你們的世界沒有藥草嗎？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100002_01.png", "speakerName": "耶魯菲莉絲", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110378_story/VO_CHR_110378_STORY_0008.wav"], "content": "嗯……要說的話雖然是有，但至少不是那種會自己去摘的東西才對……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110378_02.png", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100002_story/VO_CHR_100002_STORY_0079.wav"], "content": "這樣啊……果然不同的世界就是有許多事情都不一樣呢。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100002_01.png", "speakerName": "耶魯菲莉絲", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "總之，這座城裡有精通藥草知識的專家。就由我去拜託那個人來帶領妳吧。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100002_01.png", "speakerName": "耶魯菲莉絲", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110378_story/VO_CHR_110378_STORY_0005.wav"], "content": "謝謝妳，耶魯菲莉絲！真是幫大忙了！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110378_02.png", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100002_story/VO_CHR_100002_STORY_0004.wav"], "content": "不必客氣。如果還有其他問題的話，都儘管問。那麼，我先離開了。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100002_01.png", "speakerName": "耶魯菲莉絲", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110378_story/VO_CHR_110378_STORY_0001.wav"], "content": "耶魯菲莉絲……人很好呢。既溫柔又親切……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110378_02.png", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "好～！那我就接受她的好意，先來放鬆一下吧！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110378_02.png", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"type": "break"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110378_story/VO_CHR_110378_STORY_0023.wav"], "content": "……不行，房間太寬敞反而不自在……這個世界裡也沒有能讓我打發時間的網路或是遊戲……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110378_02.png", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "想要過像原本世界的生活，果然在這裡是不可能的……嗯～怎麼辦呢……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110378_02.png", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"type": "break"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110378_story/VO_CHR_110378_STORY_0020.wav"], "content": "……所以呢……抱歉囉，耶魯菲莉絲。我跑來找妳玩了。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110378_02.png", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100002_story/VO_CHR_100002_STORY_0040.wav"], "content": "不必在意。如果妳不嫌棄的話，我很樂意奉陪。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100002_01.png", "speakerName": "耶魯菲莉絲", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110378_story/VO_CHR_110378_STORY_0005.wav"], "content": "謝謝妳！那麼，既然機會難得，可以跟我說說妳的事嗎？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110378_02.png", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100002_story/VO_CHR_100002_STORY_0042.wav"], "content": "咦？我的事嗎……？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100002_01.png", "speakerName": "耶魯菲莉絲", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110378_story/VO_CHR_110378_STORY_0012.wav"], "content": "嗯！我想和耶魯菲莉絲變成好朋友！……會很困擾嗎？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110378_02.png", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100002_story/VO_CHR_100002_STORY_0033.wav"], "content": "……不，如果是那樣的話我很歡迎。那麼，我就再自我介紹一次……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100002_01.png", "speakerName": "耶魯菲莉絲", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "我是耶魯菲莉絲，伊利亞教會的聖騎士。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100002_01.png", "speakerName": "耶魯菲莉絲", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110378_story/VO_CHR_110378_STORY_0042.wav"], "content": "那個……伊利亞教會？聖騎士？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110378_02.png", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100002_story/VO_CHR_100002_STORY_0030.wav"], "content": "所謂的伊利亞教會，就是在這片土地上擁有權威，並掌管秩序的組織。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100002_01.png", "speakerName": "耶魯菲莉絲", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "而為了組織行使力量的，就是我們聖騎士。我們肩負著保護祭司等要人及其他各種使命。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100002_01.png", "speakerName": "耶魯菲莉絲", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110378_story/VO_CHR_110378_STORY_0079.wav"], "content": "啊！也就是保鏢囉！好帥！確實耶魯菲莉絲很符合那種感覺！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110378_02.png", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "怪盜團裡也有像耶魯菲莉絲這樣的女孩子喔！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110378_02.png", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "非常認真、溫柔、而且很強……她叫做QUEEN！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110378_02.png", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "是嗎……但是很抱歉，我其實以一名聖騎士來說並不是很稱職……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100002_01.png", "speakerName": "耶魯菲莉絲", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100002_story/VO_CHR_100002_STORY_0023.wav"], "content": "在教會的教義和自己的信念之間，我非常地煩惱……迷惘……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100002_01.png", "speakerName": "耶魯菲莉絲", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "耶魯菲莉絲……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110378_02.png", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "……但是，會煩惱、會迷惘，我覺得一點都不是可恥的事喔。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110378_02.png", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100002_story/VO_CHR_100002_STORY_0042.wav"], "content": "咦？但是……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100002_01.png", "speakerName": "耶魯菲莉絲", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110378_story/VO_CHR_110378_STORY_0030.wav"], "content": "我呢，在剛開始做模特兒的工作時，都抱著很隨便的心態。大概這樣就行了吧～這種感覺。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110378_02.png", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "然後很理所當然地，我那樣是不夠的，於是就碰壁了……讓我很煩惱、很迷惘……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110378_02.png", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "但是……正因為發生過那些事，現在我才能夠認真地作為一名模特兒去努力。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110378_02.png", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "所以囉！不管是煩惱還是迷惘，我覺得全都不必感到可恥，而且也不會沒有意義。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110378_02.png", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100002_story/VO_CHR_100002_STORY_0045.wav"], "content": "PANTHER……謝謝妳。我覺得心情比較輕鬆了。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100002_01.png", "speakerName": "耶魯菲莉絲", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "……妳真是厲害呢。能這麼正向，不管是煩惱或是迷惘，都能變成妳的動力……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100002_01.png", "speakerName": "耶魯菲莉絲", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110378_story/VO_CHR_110378_STORY_0073.wav"], "content": "嘿嘿嘿，被妳這樣說真害羞呢。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110378_02.png", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "雖然說得好像很厲害……但結果我也只是覺得自己當個半吊子的模特兒很遜而已。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110378_02.png", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100002_story/VO_CHR_100002_STORY_0079.wav"], "content": "是嗎……雖然我不是很清楚，但是要成為繪畫的模特兒，原來也是需要相當的覺悟啊。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100002_01.png", "speakerName": "耶魯菲莉絲", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110378_story/VO_CHR_110378_STORY_0042.wav"], "content": "咦！？啊，不是……不是那種模特兒，是雜誌或是照相的……怎麼說呢……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110378_02.png", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "我知道了，那我來說說我們世界的事情好了。就互相聊聊彼此的事情吧！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110378_02.png", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100002_story/VO_CHR_100002_STORY_0011.wav"], "content": "嗯，也好。我很期待能從PANTHER那邊聽到什麼有趣的事情。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100002_01.png", "speakerName": "耶魯菲莉絲", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110378_story/VO_CHR_110378_STORY_0004.wav"], "content": "好！今天就通宵聊個一整晚吧，耶魯菲莉絲！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110378_02.png", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}], "id": 110378011, "title": "異世界也要女子談話"}, {"conversations": [{"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110378_story/VO_CHR_110378_STORY_0016.wav"], "content": "嗚哇……！這個世界裡真的有很多龍族呢！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210001_01.png", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100002_story/VO_CHR_100002_STORY_0030.wav"], "content": "PANTHER的世界裡沒有龍族對吧。那麼，妳這是第一次見到龍族囉？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100002_01.png", "speakerName": "耶魯菲莉絲", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110378_story/VO_CHR_110378_STORY_0011.wav"], "content": "嗯！……啊，但是……冒牌龍族的話，最近算有看到吧。啊哈哈……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210001_01.png", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100002_story/VO_CHR_100002_STORY_0042.wav"], "content": "冒牌龍族……？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100002_01.png", "speakerName": "耶魯菲莉絲", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110378_story/VO_CHR_110378_STORY_0020.wav"], "content": "啊～不是什麼特別的事啦。妳別在意。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210001_01.png", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110378_story/VO_CHR_110378_STORY_0042.wav"], "content": "喔……好美的歌聲……這是誰在唱歌呢？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210001_01.png", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100002_story/VO_CHR_100002_STORY_0011.wav"], "content": "是賽蓮吧。她是隻歌聲優美得令人著迷的龍族。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100002_01.png", "speakerName": "耶魯菲莉絲", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110378_story/VO_CHR_110378_STORY_0006.wav"], "content": "咦咦！？這是龍族在唱歌！？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210001_01.png", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "如果妳很在意的話，那就去看看如何？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100002_01.png", "speakerName": "耶魯菲莉絲", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110378_story/VO_CHR_110378_STORY_0012.wav"], "content": "就這麼辦！那晚點見囉，耶魯菲莉絲！槍術的訓練要好好加油唷！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210001_01.png", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "～～♪", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120138_01.png", "speakerName": "賽蓮", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "賽蓮！賽蓮！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120019_01.png", "speakerName": "粉絲們", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "好厲害……簡直就像偶像在開演唱會似的……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210001_01.png", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"type": "break"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_drg_210054_story/VO_DRG_210054_STORY_0005.wav"], "content": "大家～！今天謝謝你們～！我們下次見囉～☆", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120138_01.png", "speakerName": "賽蓮", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "下次見～！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120019_01.png", "speakerName": "粉絲們", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110378_story/VO_CHR_110378_STORY_0017.wav"], "content": "好有人氣喔！賽蓮妳該不會是這個世界的頂級偶像吧？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210001_01.png", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_drg_210054_story/VO_DRG_210054_STORY_0042.wav"], "content": "偶像……？那是什麼？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120138_01.png", "speakerName": "賽蓮", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110378_story/VO_CHR_110378_STORY_0042.wav"], "content": "咦，不是嗎？但是……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210001_01.png", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "……？啊、我懂了。這個世界裡可能也不是叫做偶像……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210001_01.png", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "嗯嗯？這個世界……？啊，該不會～☆", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120138_01.png", "speakerName": "賽蓮", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "就是妳吧！？我聽說有來自異界的怪盜！！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120138_01.png", "speakerName": "賽蓮", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110378_story/VO_CHR_110378_STORY_0011.wav"], "content": "嗯，我是PANTHER。請多指教囉。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210001_01.png", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_drg_210054_story/VO_DRG_210054_STORY_0080.wav"], "content": "請多指教！我叫做賽蓮☆所以呢所以呢，偶像是什麼？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120138_01.png", "speakerName": "賽蓮", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110378_story/VO_CHR_110378_STORY_0030.wav"], "content": "那個啊……就像是照亮大家的光芒一樣，比任何人都還耀眼……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210001_01.png", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "給予脆弱或是消沉的人們笑容與活力的存在……大概是這樣吧。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210001_01.png", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "是這樣啊……！也許有點像呢！我也是想透過唱歌、跳舞，來讓大家開心！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120138_01.png", "speakerName": "賽蓮", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "吶、吶！該不會PANTHER就是偶像吧！？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120138_01.png", "speakerName": "賽蓮", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110378_story/VO_CHR_110378_STORY_0033.wav"], "content": "不，我是模特兒……就算這麼說，應該也無法理解吧……總之，我不是偶像就對了。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210001_01.png", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_drg_210054_story/VO_DRG_210054_STORY_0079.wav"], "content": "這樣啊，真遺憾……本來想說是偶像的話，就可以請教妳許多事情了。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120138_01.png", "speakerName": "賽蓮", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "抱歉囉，賽蓮。……啊，但是，舞台動作我倒是可以教妳唷。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210001_01.png", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "畢竟瞬間擺出亮眼的姿勢，就是模特兒的工作！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210001_01.png", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_drg_210054_story/VO_DRG_210054_STORY_0004.wav"], "content": "太好了，拜託妳教教我怎麼擺出亮眼的姿勢吧！這樣我就能讓大家更開心了☆", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120138_01.png", "speakerName": "賽蓮", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110378_story/VO_CHR_110378_STORY_0012.wav"], "content": "好喔！那麼，現在就教妳馬上就能學會的擺姿勢祕訣！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210001_01.png", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "首先是鐵則……！到每個指尖為止，所有細節都要意識到！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210001_01.png", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "挺直地伸出，流暢地彎曲……如果指尖的姿態不好看，會讓妳全身的動作都不好看！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210001_01.png", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_drg_210054_story/VO_DRG_210054_STORY_0084.wav"], "content": "嗯嗯……！像這樣嗎？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120138_01.png", "speakerName": "賽蓮", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110378_story/VO_CHR_110378_STORY_0017.wav"], "content": "沒錯沒錯！很棒、很棒！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210001_01.png", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "然後，視線也很重要！光是眼神的不同，表情看起來就會有相當大的變化。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210001_01.png", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_drg_210054_story/VO_DRG_210054_STORY_0018.wav"], "content": "是這樣啊……！好厲害～☆那些事情我從來都沒想過耶！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120138_01.png", "speakerName": "賽蓮", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110378_story/VO_CHR_110378_STORY_0001.wav"], "content": "呵呵，有幫上妳的忙真是太好了！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210001_01.png", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_drg_210054_story/VO_DRG_210054_STORY_0005.wav"], "content": "謝謝妳，PANTHER！我學到了好多喔☆", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120138_01.png", "speakerName": "賽蓮", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "啊，作為回禮，我就教妳唱歌跳舞吧☆", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120138_01.png", "speakerName": "賽蓮", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110378_story/VO_CHR_110378_STORY_0022.wav"], "content": "真的嗎？那麼可以好好教我怎麼跳舞嗎？對模特兒擺姿勢來說應該也會有幫助！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210001_01.png", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_drg_210054_story/VO_DRG_210054_STORY_0012.wav"], "content": "OK～☆那麼，舞步的訣竅是……！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120138_01.png", "speakerName": "賽蓮", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110378_story/VO_CHR_110378_STORY_0058.wav"], "content": "嗯嗯……像這樣嗎？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210001_01.png", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "（呵呵……好開心！）", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210001_01.png", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "（想不到居然能和龍族像這樣變成朋友……！能來到這世界，真是太好了！）", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210001_01.png", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}], "id": 110378012, "title": "異世界的偶像"}, {"conversations": [{"audioPaths": [], "content": "啊，找到了！這就是藥草喔，PANTHER！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100006_01.png", "speakerName": "琉卡", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110378_story/VO_CHR_110378_STORY_0005.wav"], "content": "謝謝你，琉卡！好，那就來大採特採吧！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110378_02.png", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "這世界沒有藥妝店，我還想說到底傷藥要怎麼辦……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110378_02.png", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "但沒想到藥草這東西，一找之下其實有不少呢。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110378_02.png", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100006_story/VO_CHR_100006_STORY_0004.wav"], "content": "嘿嘿！我們佛萊斯提亞可是森林子民。只要跟森林有關的事，我們全都知道！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100006_01.png", "speakerName": "琉卡", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "這個藥草的話，走到更深處應該還有很多。我們就去看看吧！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100006_01.png", "speakerName": "琉卡", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110378_story/VO_CHR_110378_STORY_0042.wav"], "content": "咦？再到更深處去？沒事嗎……？不會迷路吧……？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110378_02.png", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100006_story/VO_CHR_100006_STORY_0040.wav"], "content": "跟妳說沒事啦！森林裡面就跟我家的後院沒什麼兩樣！來，我們走吧！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100006_01.png", "speakerName": "琉卡", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "嗯、嗯……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110378_02.png", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"type": "break"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "右邊沒問題、左邊沒問題……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110378_02.png", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100006_story/VO_CHR_100006_STORY_0043.wav"], "content": "嗯？妳怎麼這麼警戒呀？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100006_01.png", "speakerName": "琉卡", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "這邊離埃米爾的監獄很遠，而且也沒出現那個叫做陰影的東西不是嗎？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100006_01.png", "speakerName": "琉卡", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110378_story/VO_CHR_110378_STORY_0008.wav"], "content": "是那樣沒錯……但不是有可能會出現魔獸嗎……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110378_02.png", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "而且又是在森林深處……有種就是會冒出什麼的感覺……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110378_02.png", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100006_story/VO_CHR_100006_STORY_0008.wav"], "content": "嗯～我覺得是沒必要擔心喔！畢竟沒有看到類似的跡象。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100006_01.png", "speakerName": "琉卡", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "而且也沒有足跡，樹枝也沒折斷……總而言之，應該就可以認定這附近沒有大型魔獸了吧。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100006_01.png", "speakerName": "琉卡", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110378_story/VO_CHR_110378_STORY_0036.wav"], "content": "是、是這樣啊？那就太好了……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110378_02.png", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "先不說那些了！妳來看這個，PANTHER！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100006_01.png", "speakerName": "琉卡", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "什麼什麼？找到藥草了嗎？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110378_02.png", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100006_story/VO_CHR_100006_STORY_0019.wav"], "content": "我找到蘋果了喔！這看起來超好吃的對吧！？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100006_01.png", "speakerName": "琉卡", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110378_story/VO_CHR_110378_STORY_0002.wav"], "content": "真是的……！琉卡，現在的目的不是找蘋果吧！？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110378_02.png", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100006_story/VO_CHR_100006_STORY_0004.wav"], "content": "不不！這如果現在不採它，一定會後悔的！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100006_01.png", "speakerName": "琉卡", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "妳看仔細了，看它有多水嫩多汁！這蘋果看起來超棒的吧！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100006_01.png", "speakerName": "琉卡", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110378_story/VO_CHR_110378_STORY_0023.wav"], "content": "唉……蘋果就是蘋果吧……有什麼好那麼驚奇的……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110378_02.png", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110378_story/VO_CHR_110378_STORY_0006.wav"], "content": "……等等，它真的在閃閃發亮耶！咕唔……看、看起來很好吃……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110378_02.png", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "喔？PANTHER也想吃看看嗎？好，那我就分妳一半吧！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100006_01.png", "speakerName": "琉卡", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110378_story/VO_CHR_110378_STORY_0066.wav"], "content": "真的嗎！？謝謝！那我就不客氣了……我咬。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110378_02.png", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110378_story/VO_CHR_110378_STORY_0085.wav"], "content": "嗯～～！好甜～！好好吃～！又脆味道又香甜……！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110378_02.png", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "雖然上面放了滿滿鮮奶油的甜點很棒，但這種新鮮的天然甘甜也相當好呢！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110378_02.png", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "真的是太棒了！我沒吃過這樣子的蘋果……！！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110378_02.png", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100006_story/VO_CHR_100006_STORY_0030.wav"], "content": "搞不好是因為這座森林裡，充滿了良質的瑪納。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100006_01.png", "speakerName": "琉卡", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110378_story/VO_CHR_110378_STORY_0042.wav"], "content": "瑪納……？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110378_02.png", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "啊，這樣啊。PANTHER你們的世界裡沒有瑪納對吧。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100006_01.png", "speakerName": "琉卡", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "那個，總之……這顆蘋果會這麼好吃，都是大自然的恩惠啦。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100006_01.png", "speakerName": "琉卡", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110378_story/VO_CHR_110378_STORY_0016.wav"], "content": "大自然的恩惠……！？我說，該不會……！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110378_02.png", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "並不是這顆蘋果特別甜……而是這森林裡的蘋果全都這麼甜吧！？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110378_02.png", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100006_story/VO_CHR_100006_STORY_0011.wav"], "content": "嗯，我猜是那樣沒錯喔。所以得多採一些回去才行了！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100006_01.png", "speakerName": "琉卡", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110378_story/VO_CHR_110378_STORY_0001.wav"], "content": "沒錯！就盡量採多一點回去，讓克菈兒把它做成甜點吧！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110378_02.png", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"type": "break"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110378_story/VO_CHR_110378_STORY_0004.wav"], "content": "啊哈哈！採到好多喔！已經要拿不動了！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110378_02.png", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100006_story/VO_CHR_100006_STORY_0004.wav"], "content": "我也是！這樣就有好禮物能帶回去給城裡的大家了！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100006_01.png", "speakerName": "琉卡", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110378_story/VO_CHR_110378_STORY_0012.wav"], "content": "你說得對！……那麼，我們回去吧！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110378_02.png", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100006_story/VO_CHR_100006_STORY_0042.wav"], "content": "嗯！……等等，我們沒忘記什麼事吧……？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100006_01.png", "speakerName": "琉卡", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110378_story/VO_CHR_110378_STORY_0008.wav"], "content": "被你這麼一說……我好像也忘了什麼重要的事……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110378_02.png", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "……啊啊！？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "PANTHER＆琉卡", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "想起來了！我們是來採藥草的啊！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110378_02.png", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100006_story/VO_CHR_100006_STORY_0064.wav"], "content": "糟糕……！太專心在採蘋果了！結果天都要黑了！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100006_01.png", "speakerName": "琉卡", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "就算有我在，夜晚的森林還是太危險了！不小心還會迷路……！我們趕緊採藥草吧！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100006_01.png", "speakerName": "琉卡", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110378_story/VO_CHR_110378_STORY_0002.wav"], "content": "真是的！！竟然有這種甜蜜陷阱！搞不好這裡比監獄還要危險啊！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110378_02.png", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}], "id": 110378013, "title": "異世界的自然恩惠"}, {"conversations": [{"audioPaths": [], "content": "事情發生在擊退魔獸的歸途，PANTHER與聖城的夥伴們來到村莊找尋過夜之處時──", "isSys": true, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "SYS", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120014_story/VO_CHR_120014_STORY_0008.wav"], "content": "啊啊……這下糟了……從今以後，該怎麼辦才好……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120014_01.png", "speakerName": "村裡的男性", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110378_story/VO_CHR_110378_STORY_0008.wav"], "content": "村裡的人們，大家臉色都好凝重……是不是發生什麼事了……？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110378_02.png", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120014_story/VO_CHR_120014_STORY_0042.wav"], "content": "喔？你們幾位……我沒見過呢。是來旅行的人嗎？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120014_01.png", "speakerName": "村裡的男性", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100006_story/VO_CHR_100006_STORY_0011.wav"], "content": "嗯，我們原本是想來找地方借住的……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100006_01.png", "speakerName": "琉卡", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "但看來，現在不是那種時候呢。到底發生什麼事了？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100006_01.png", "speakerName": "琉卡", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120014_story/VO_CHR_120014_STORY_0011.wav"], "content": "……是龍族啊。有隻在村莊附近的龍族突然就出現了……而且要求我們交出活祭品……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120014_01.png", "speakerName": "村裡的男性", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110378_story/VO_CHR_110378_STORY_0006.wav"], "content": "龍族！？但是，龍族不是人類的夥伴嗎……！？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110378_02.png", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "在聖城裡遇到的龍族們，就從沒說要活祭品……！！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110378_02.png", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "龍族之中也是有各式各樣的傢伙存在呢……並不是所有龍族都會和人類親近的。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100006_01.png", "speakerName": "琉卡", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "但是……如果跟他們說別來要求活祭品的話呢？畢竟他們也不是沒辦法用言語溝通……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110378_02.png", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120014_story/VO_CHR_120014_STORY_0002.wav"], "content": "如、如果做出那種事，得罪了龍族該怎麼辦啊！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120014_01.png", "speakerName": "村裡的男性", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110378_story/VO_CHR_110378_STORY_0042.wav"], "content": "他們會生氣……然後作亂嗎？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110378_02.png", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100002_story/VO_CHR_100002_STORY_0033.wav"], "content": "不是的，PANTHER。這個世界的人們……尤其人類，是非常崇拜龍族的。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100002_01.png", "speakerName": "耶魯菲莉絲", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "龍族司掌著瑪納與自然力量，所以是特別的存在。天災、或者是大自然的恩惠，都源自於龍族。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100002_01.png", "speakerName": "耶魯菲莉絲", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "就是這樣……如果沒有龍族的話，大地就會荒蕪，河川也會乾涸……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120014_01.png", "speakerName": "村裡的男性", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120014_story/VO_CHR_120014_STORY_0023.wav"], "content": "我們人類，只能順從龍族來活下去了……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120014_01.png", "speakerName": "村裡的男性", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110378_story/VO_CHR_110378_STORY_0037.wav"], "content": "怎麼這樣……所以只能忍耐的意思？就算因為龍族而遭受不幸……也就只能忍氣吞聲、放棄抵抗……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110378_02.png", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "是啊……這就如同是這世界的定律一般……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100002_01.png", "speakerName": "耶魯菲莉絲", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "這世界的定律……不得不遵守的規則……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110378_02.png", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "（那麼，或許就不是我這個外人可以隨便插手的事情……）", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110378_02.png", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "（……但是，這樣……真的好嗎……？）", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110378_02.png", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110378_story/VO_CHR_110378_STORY_0042.wav"], "content": "嗯……？那兩個人，是怎麼了……？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110378_02.png", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120018_story/VO_CHR_120018_STORY_0034.wav"], "content": "我會為了妳去當活祭品的！所以，妳要活下去……！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120018_01.png", "speakerName": "村裡的少女", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120056_story/VO_CHR_120056_STORY_0038.wav"], "content": "不、不可以那樣……！被選為活祭品的是我！妳沒有必要犧牲……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120056_01.png", "speakerName": "少女的朋友", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120018_story/VO_CHR_120018_STORY_0038.wav"], "content": "但是……我辦不到！眼看著朋友去當活祭品這種事……！！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120018_01.png", "speakerName": "村裡的少女", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "（……！那兩人，和以前的我們一樣……！）", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110378_02.png", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "（那時候我為了志帆……然後……志帆也為了我……）", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110378_02.png", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "（我們都覺得只要是能幫助朋友，即使犧牲自己也無所謂……）", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110378_02.png", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110378_story/VO_CHR_110378_STORY_0011.wav"], "content": "……決定了！我果然忍不下這口氣！我要去找龍族，叫他放棄活祭品！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110378_02.png", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "就算要阻止我也沒用喔，耶魯菲莉絲！琉卡！就算只有我一個人……！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110378_02.png", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100006_story/VO_CHR_100006_STORY_0033.wav"], "content": "……不，我們不會阻止妳啦。讓我們也一起去吧！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100006_01.png", "speakerName": "琉卡", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110378_story/VO_CHR_110378_STORY_0042.wav"], "content": "咦？但是……那不是這個世界的定律嗎……！？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110378_02.png", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100006_story/VO_CHR_100006_STORY_0004.wav"], "content": "嘿嘿！我已經很習慣打破定律了嘛！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100006_01.png", "speakerName": "琉卡", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "我也有話想對這裡的龍族說！所以，就一起去找他吧，PANTHER！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100006_01.png", "speakerName": "琉卡", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100002_story/VO_CHR_100002_STORY_0025.wav"], "content": "喂、喂，你們兩個……！……沒辦法，我也一起同行吧。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100002_01.png", "speakerName": "耶魯菲莉絲", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "畢竟在你們想要亂來的時候，要是沒有人阻止你們，大概會變成很糟糕的狀況……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100002_01.png", "speakerName": "耶魯菲莉絲", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110378_story/VO_CHR_110378_STORY_0046.wav"], "content": "琉卡……！耶魯菲莉絲……！謝謝你們！這樣我安心多了！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110378_02.png", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"type": "break"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100006_story/VO_CHR_100006_STORY_0010.wav"], "content": "喂！龍族！你在吧？快給我出來～！！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100006_01.png", "speakerName": "琉卡", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "（嗚哇……！這龍族怎麼看起來就很恐怖……！？）", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110378_02.png", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "（但、但是……！我可不能退縮。一定要好好說清楚……！）", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110378_02.png", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110378_story/VO_CHR_110378_STORY_0058.wav"], "content": "那、那個……！我們有些話想跟你說……！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110378_02.png", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "嗯……有話要跟我說嗎？好吧，我歡迎你們幾位。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210011_01.png", "speakerName": "斯特利伯格", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110378_story/VO_CHR_110378_STORY_0042.wav"], "content": "咦……？意外地很紳士……？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110378_02.png", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100006_story/VO_CHR_100006_STORY_0030.wav"], "content": "就是說啊……都講出活祭品這種話了，我還以為會是個更粗魯的傢伙……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100006_01.png", "speakerName": "琉卡", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "活祭品……？你們到底在說什麼？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210011_01.png", "speakerName": "斯特利伯格", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110378_story/VO_CHR_110378_STORY_0002.wav"], "content": "你、你在村子裡說了那種話吧！？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110378_02.png", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "……？確實我到村子裡去了，但那種事我一個字也沒提到……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210011_01.png", "speakerName": "斯特利伯格", "type": "conversation"}, {"type": "break"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110378_story/VO_CHR_110378_STORY_0079.wav"], "content": "……原來如此。也就是說，只是村子裡的人誤解了而已啊。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110378_02.png", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "嗯，我從太古時代就隱遁於這洞窟裡，獨自思索著各種事情……但幾天前突然有個念頭。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210011_01.png", "speakerName": "斯特利伯格", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "我想是否與相異於自己的存在……也就是人類之子交談，就能讓我的思考更加全面。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210011_01.png", "speakerName": "斯特利伯格", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100002_story/VO_CHR_100002_STORY_0079.wav"], "content": "所以是想要找到談話的對象，結果被村民們擅自誤會成是要找活祭品……這樣嗎？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100002_01.png", "speakerName": "耶魯菲莉絲", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100006_story/VO_CHR_100006_STORY_0023.wav"], "content": "真是的……村子裡的那些傢伙。誤會這種會造成騷動的事情。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100006_01.png", "speakerName": "琉卡", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110378_story/VO_CHR_110378_STORY_0020.wav"], "content": "啊哈哈……一定是因為嚇呆了，完全陷入驚恐之中了吧……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110378_02.png", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "（我一開始的時候也是那樣……）", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110378_02.png", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100006_story/VO_CHR_100006_STORY_0043.wav"], "content": "嗯？怎麼了，PANTHER？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100006_01.png", "speakerName": "琉卡", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110378_story/VO_CHR_110378_STORY_0033.wav"], "content": "沒、沒什麼事！比起那個，我們快回村子裡去解開這場誤會吧！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110378_02.png", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"type": "break"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120014_story/VO_CHR_120014_STORY_0056.wav"], "content": "過、過來了！是龍族……！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120014_01.png", "speakerName": "村裡的男性", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120056_story/VO_CHR_120056_STORY_0037.wav"], "content": "啊啊……居然這麼快……但是，我必須得成為活祭品……！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120056_01.png", "speakerName": "少女的朋友", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120018_story/VO_CHR_120018_STORY_0038.wav"], "content": "不要……！不可以！要活祭品的話，就讓我來……！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120018_01.png", "speakerName": "村裡的少女", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110378_story/VO_CHR_110378_STORY_0054.wav"], "content": "大家等等！那是一場誤會！其實是不需要活祭品的！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110378_02.png", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "沒有錯！全都是你們誤會了！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100006_01.png", "speakerName": "琉卡", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "什、什麼……？這是怎麼回事？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120014_01.png", "speakerName": "村裡的男性", "type": "conversation"}, {"type": "break"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110378_story/VO_CHR_110378_STORY_0024.wav"], "content": "……呼，誤會能解開真是太好了……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110378_02.png", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100002_story/VO_CHR_100002_STORY_0011.wav"], "content": "嗯，在我們的說明下，村民們終於冷靜下來，好好聽龍族說話了。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100002_01.png", "speakerName": "耶魯菲莉絲", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "受你們幫助了。多虧這樣，與村民們的對談也能迅速地進行下去。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210011_01.png", "speakerName": "斯特利伯格", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "同時也約定好了……讓大家輪流來找我交談。真的是非常感謝。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210011_01.png", "speakerName": "斯特利伯格", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110378_story/VO_CHR_110378_STORY_0001.wav"], "content": "不必客氣。太好了呢，斯特利伯格。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110378_02.png", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "還有……那邊的兩位也是。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110378_02.png", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120018_story/VO_CHR_120018_STORY_0038.wav"], "content": "嗚嗚……嘶。太好了……真的，太好了……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120018_01.png", "speakerName": "村裡的少女", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120056_story/VO_CHR_120056_STORY_0038.wav"], "content": "嗯……！我們可以在一起……一直……都在一起了呢……！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120056_01.png", "speakerName": "少女的朋友", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "（朋友間能一起在歡笑中度過的日子……是比什麼都重要的寶物呢。）", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110378_02.png", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "（……沒錯吧？志帆……）", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110378_02.png", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}], "id": 110378014, "title": "異世界中發起反抗"}, {"conversations": [{"audioPaths": [], "content": "……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110378_02.png", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110377_story/VO_CHR_110377_STORY_0043.wav"], "content": "在煩惱什麼嗎，PANTHER？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110377_02.png", "speakerName": "JOKER", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "……啊，JOKER。不是……與其說是煩惱，是在思考一點事情。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110378_02.png", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "我呢，在剛來到這個世界時，覺得這裡和我們的世界完全不同……所以真的覺得很困惑。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110378_02.png", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "畢竟你看，有真正的王子，還有龍族耶！而且還有這麼大的一座城。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110378_02.png", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110377_story/VO_CHR_110377_STORY_0011.wav"], "content": "確實是呢。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110377_02.png", "speakerName": "JOKER", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "……所以呢，當時也有一點不安。擔心在這裡能不能順利……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110378_02.png", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110378_story/VO_CHR_110378_STORY_0030.wav"], "content": "但是……結果是沒問題。因為城裡的大家，都有接納我……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110378_02.png", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "耶魯菲莉絲，她真的很溫柔……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110378_02.png", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"type": "break"}, {"type": "break"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110378_story/VO_CHR_110378_STORY_0001.wav"], "content": "與身為龍族的賽蓮，也能大聊偶像的話題……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110378_02.png", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"type": "break"}, {"type": "break"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110378_story/VO_CHR_110378_STORY_0011.wav"], "content": "琉卡很隨和，非常好相處……！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110378_02.png", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"type": "break"}, {"type": "break"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "我就這麼和在這裡遇見的人，一起到處認識了這個世界……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110378_02.png", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110378_story/VO_CHR_110378_STORY_0012.wav"], "content": "然後呢！我就發覺到了！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110378_02.png", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "我原本以為這個世界完全不同……但其實人都是一樣的！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110378_02.png", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "大家也都各自抱持著煩惱……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110378_02.png", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "自己怎樣也無法改變……如同世界規則一般的事物有時候就是會將自己給擊潰……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110378_02.png", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"type": "break"}, {"type": "break"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "即使這樣，大家……還是努力地活著。這種事情，即使到了不同世界，卻也和我們都一樣。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110378_02.png", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110378_story/VO_CHR_110378_STORY_0030.wav"], "content": "所以呢，這和交易什麼的都無關……我想要幫助這個世界的人們！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110378_02.png", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "埃米爾他從努力活著的人身上奪取『願望』，我們絕對要阻止他！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110378_02.png", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110378_story/VO_CHR_110378_STORY_0001.wav"], "content": "……就是這樣，我已經下定決心了！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110378_02.png", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110377_story/VO_CHR_110377_STORY_0079.wav"], "content": "真符合PANTHER的作風呢。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110377_02.png", "speakerName": "JOKER", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110378_story/VO_CHR_110378_STORY_0005.wav"], "content": "嘿嘿……謝謝！你一直以來都是這樣，在我的背後給我鼓勵！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110378_02.png", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "只要有JOKER在，就如同有百人的戰力！我們心之怪盜團是無敵的！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110378_02.png", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110377_story/VO_CHR_110377_STORY_0033.wav"], "content": "……並不是只有我們。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110377_02.png", "speakerName": "JOKER", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110378_story/VO_CHR_110378_STORY_0042.wav"], "content": "咦？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110378_02.png", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "現在，他們也是我們的夥伴。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110377_02.png", "speakerName": "JOKER", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0010.wav"], "content": "兩位在這啊，我正在找你們喔！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "我們差不多要前往埃米爾的監獄了。你們準備好了嗎？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110377_story/VO_CHR_110377_STORY_0011.wav"], "content": "嗯。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110377_02.png", "speakerName": "JOKER", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "是啊……！現在聖城裡的大家也都是夥伴呢！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110378_02.png", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "我也是，隨時都可以出發喔，尤蒂爾！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110378_02.png", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110378_story/VO_CHR_110378_STORY_0082.wav"], "content": "心之怪盜團與聖城的夥伴們……一起合力去拯救這個世界的人吧！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110378_02.png", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}], "id": 110378015, "title": "異世界之決心"}]